  "id": "RAW_5d0ac6",
  "title": "腾讯混元自研深度思考模型「T1」正式发布",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/38ilIogkFK8tbgRFDSXdSw",
  "date": "2025-03-21 15:15:06",
  "author": "腾讯混元",
  "siteName": "腾讯混元",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">今天，我们正式推出自研深度思考模型<strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 82, 217);\">混元T1正式版</span></strong>。</span><o:p></o:p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">「T1」吐字快、能秒回，还擅长超长文处理，是腾讯自研的强推理模型，已经上线腾讯云，即将在腾讯元宝灰度上线。</span><o:p></o:p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">通过大规模强化学习，并结合数学、逻辑推理、科学和代码等理科难题的专项优化，混元T1正式版进一步提升了推理能力。</span>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-galleryid=\"\" data-imgfileid=\"100010713\" data-ratio=\"0.8018518518518518\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a7a97ba9-6c41-4870-2283-c8a2dc613700/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/a7a97ba9-6c41-4870-2283-c8a2dc613700/public\"></p>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <o:p></o:p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">在体现推理模型基础能力的常见benchmark上，如大语言模型评估增强数据集MMLU-PRO中，混元T1取得87.2分，仅次于o1。在CEval、AIME、Zebra Logic等中英文知识及竞赛级数学、逻辑推理的公开基准测试中，混元T1的成绩也达到业界领先推理模型的水平。</span><o:p></o:p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">「T1」还在多项对齐任务、指令跟随任务和工具利用任务中展现出了非常强的适应性。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"text-align: center;margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-cropselx1=\"0\" data-cropselx2=\"477\" data-cropsely1=\"0\" data-cropsely2=\"324\" data-imgfileid=\"100010702\" data-ratio=\"0.6805555555555556\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/01b5a0ba-2189-4ccf-01e7-747cb740b700/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" style=\"width: 477px;height: 325px;\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/01b5a0ba-2189-4ccf-01e7-747cb740b700/public\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100010703\" data-ratio=\"0.7194444444444444\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/74a9a559-7cb0-46ee-295f-19c076bfe300/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" height=\"358.173\" style=\"font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;width: 497.974px;height: 358.173px;\" width=\"497.974\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/74a9a559-7cb0-46ee-295f-19c076bfe300/public\">\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(136, 136, 136);font-size: 14px;\">注：表格中，其它模型的评测指标来自官方评测结果，官方评测结果中没有的部分来自混元内部评测平台结果</span><o:p></o:p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">混元T1正式版沿用了混元Turbo S的创新架构，采用Hybrid-Mamba-Transformer 融合模式。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 217);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这是工业界首次将混合Mamba架构无损应用于超大型推理模型。</span></strong></span><o:p></o:p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100010701\" data-ratio=\"0.5193312434691745\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/32c66971-e428-436f-09b5-31d55a6d5c00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"957\" height=\"314.057\" style=\"width: 604.733px;height: 314.057px;\" width=\"604.733\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/32c66971-e428-436f-09b5-31d55a6d5c00/public\"><o:p></o:p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">这一架构有效降低了传统Transformer结构的计算复杂度，减少了KV-Cache的内存占用，从而<span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 82, 217);\"><strong>显著降低了训练和推理成本</strong></span>。</span><o:p></o:p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">混元T1在超长文本推理领域也展现出独特优势。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">基于出色的长文捕捉能力，混元T1能有效解决长文推理中常见的上下文丢失和长距离信息依赖问题。同时，混合Mamba架构针对长序列处理进行了专项优化，通过高效的计算方式，在确保长文本信息捕捉能力的同时大幅降低资源消耗，在相近的激活参数量下，<strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 217);\">实现了解码速度提升</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 17px;\"><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 217);\">2</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 82, 217);\">倍</span></strong>。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100010700\" data-ratio=\"0.4660734149054505\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d493c95a-a998-445d-2c43-5768404f9600/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"899\" height=\"281.85\" style=\"width: 604.733px;height: 281.85px;\" width=\"604.733\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/d493c95a-a998-445d-2c43-5768404f9600/public\"><o:p></o:p>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 82, 217);\">【抢先体验】</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">想使用体验<span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 82, 217);\"><strong>「快快快快快」</strong></span>腾讯混元T1，戳👇或点击<strong>阅读原文</strong>直接体验：</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <strong style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 217);font-size: 15px;letter-spacing: 0.578px;\">https://llm.hunyuan.tencent.com/#/chat/hy-t1</strong>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"color: rgb(0, 82, 217);\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 15px;\">【API使用】</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">混元T1已在腾讯云官网上线「输入价格为每百万tokens 1元，输出价格为每百万tokens 4元」。</span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"></span><span style=\"font-size: 15px;font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;\">企业用户需求请扫码或点击链接申请试用，戳👇：</span><strong style=\"font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;letter-spacing: 0.034em;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 82, 217);\">https://cloud.tencent.com/apply/p/jevgtnvuh3</span></strong>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <span style=\"font-size: 15px;\"><strong style=\"font-family: mp-quote, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: var(--articleFontsize);letter-spacing: 0.034em;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;color: rgb(0, 82, 217);\"></span></strong></span>\n  </section>\n  <section style=\"margin-left: 8px;margin-right: 8px;\">\n   <img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100010704\" data-ratio=\"1\" data-src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6eab8949-0b0d-43f3-0ba4-0f6d7cdfab00/public\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"144\" height=\"144\" style=\"width: 144px;height: 144px;\" width=\"144\" src=\"https://imagedelivery.net/qGOFcc1O8XwTZW3W1JAHHg/6eab8949-0b0d-43f3-0ba4-0f6d7cdfab00/public\"><o:p></o:p>\n  </section>\n  <p style=\"display: none;\"><mp-style-type data-value=\"3\"></mp-style-type></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "腾讯发布自研深度思考模型混元 T1 正式版，该模型采用混合架构，擅长长文本处理和复杂推理，在多个基准测试中表现出色，致力于解决实际问题。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "腾讯发布自研深度思考模型混元 T1 正式版，该模型采用混合架构，擅长长文本处理和复杂推理，在多个基准测试中表现出色，致力于解决实际问题。",
  "summary": "腾讯正式发布了自研深度思考模型混元 T1 正式版，针对传统 Transformer 模型的计算复杂度和长文本处理瓶颈，该模型通过大规模强化学习和针对理科难题的专项优化，显著提升了推理能力，在 MMLU-PRO 等基准测试中表现优异。混元 T1 沿用了混元 Turbo S 的创新架构，首次将混合 Mamba 架构无损应用于超大型推理模型，有效降低了计算复杂度和内存占用，从而降低了训练和推理成本。此外，混元 T1 在超长文本推理方面也表现出独特优势，通过高效的计算方式，在确保长文本信息捕捉能力的同时大幅降低资源消耗，解码速度提升 2 倍。目前，混元 T1 已在腾讯云上线，并提供 API 使用，标志着腾讯在 AI 大模型领域的商业化进程又迈出重要一步。",
